S-seats are in the front of the 1st-floor arena, A-seats are in the back of the 1st floor and the front of the 2nd and 3rd floors, and B-seats are divided between the 3rd and 4th floors.

749
00:54:43,127 --> 00:54:46,527
続いてお楽しみのグッズ情報になります。
Next is the much-anticipated goods information.

750
00:54:46,627 --> 00:54:52,127
グッズもこの後21時より販売開始です。まずは「応援セット」のご紹介です。
Goods will also go on sale at 9:00 PM. First, let me introduce the "Support Set".

751
00:54:52,227 --> 00:55:00,127
35Pライト、Tシャツ、たすき風タオル、そしてセット特典のリストバンドが入っているセットになります。
This set includes the 35P Light, T-shirt, sash-style towel, and a wristband as a set bonus.

752
00:55:00,142 --> 00:55:20,142
応援セット
Support Set

753
00:55:00,242 --> 00:55:01,942
11,300円ですね。
It's 11,300 yen.

754
00:55:02,642 --> 00:55:08,642
えー、まあこちらはですね、やっぱみこPライトはもうみんなね、絶対ゲットしなきゃいけないよねっていうのと、
Well, as for this, everyone absolutely has to get the MikoP Light, right? And...

755
00:55:09,142 --> 00:55:15,642
タオルもですね、こだわり、こだわりを詰め込んだので、みんなぜひこれをね、装着して着てくださいね。
I've packed the towel with my personal touches, so everyone, please wear it and come see me!

756
00:55:16,942 --> 00:55:19,942
それぞれのグッズは単品でも販売します。
Each of these items will also be sold individually.

757
00:55:20,142 --> 00:55:41,642
先行発送グッズ
Pre-order Shipping Items

758
00:55:20,642 --> 00:55:26,642
今回、みこPはっぴも、先行発送対象となります。やったー！
This time, the MikoP Happi is also eligible for pre-order shipping. Yay!

